V0509_01_00_00_0.text:
I'm Lulu Obsidian.
It's nice to meet you.

V0509_01_00_01_0.text: Remember the #1 rule of Dueling: To have fun!

V0509_01_00_02_0.text: I want my Duel to make everyone smile too!

V0509_01_00_03_0.text: If we give it our all, this Duel is going to be great!

V0509_01_00_04_0.text: I'll keep working hard to become the Duelist I want to be!

V0509_01_00_05_0.text: I won't lose that easily either!

V0509_01_00_06_0.text: Let's make the whole world smile with our Dueling, Yuto!

V0509_01_00_07_0.text: You may know my Deck, but I know yours too, Shay!

V0509_01_00_08_0.text:
Kite!?
What are you doing here...?

V0509_01_00_09_0.text:
It feels weird to Duel you...
But I'm still going to win!

V0509_03_00_01_0.text: I have the advantage, but I have to keep on my toes!

V0509_03_00_04_0.text: You've done whatever you like - but no more!

V0509_03_00_05_0.text:
It's not over yet!
Not as long as I have a say!

V0509_05_00_00_0.text:
I believe in my Deck.
And I know my Deck believes in me!

V0509_06_01_01_0.text: I won't let you do that!

V0509_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0509_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0509_11_08_01_0.text:
I build the Overlay Network!
Xyz Summon!

V0509_16_00_01_0.text: This attack will end the Duel!

V0509_21_00_00_0.text: This is good enough for now...

V0509_21_00_01_0.text: I can't let my guard down...

V0509_21_00_03_0.text: With that, I end my turn!

V0509_21_00_04_0.text: I have to find a way to win...

V0509_21_00_05_0.text: I just need to survive for now!

V0509_28_00_00_0.text: This Duel made me feel like I was soaring through the sky.

V0509_28_00_01_0.text: We Duel to make friends - not enemies.

V0509_28_00_02_0.text:
Phew...
I wasn't sure I could win...

V0509_28_00_03_0.text: Spade School's pretty competitive, so we all try to win.

V0509_28_00_04_0.text:
This Duel completely wiped me out.
I could use a nap.

V0509_28_00_05_0.text: I wanna Duel like I'm singing through the wind.

V0509_28_00_06_0.text: Yuto and my brother had to fight hard to save me.

V0509_28_00_06_1.text: But from now on, I hope we can all Duel just for fun.

V0509_28_00_07_0.text:
Don't worry so much.
Yuto's looking after me too, remember?

V0509_29_00_00_0.text:
I lost...
But that was so exciting!

V0509_29_00_01_0.text:
I didn't stand a chance...
But I won't lose next time!

V0509_29_00_02_0.text: How did you know so much about my Lyrilusc Deck?

V0509_29_00_03_0.text: If I want to make everyone happy, I have to get stronger!

V0509_29_00_04_0.text: I guess you don't need to change your strategy if it works.

V0509_29_00_05_0.text:
Duel to make everyone smile...
You kept our promise, Yuto.

V0509_29_00_06_0.text:
Sigh...
You're just too good, Shay.

V0509_29_00_07_0.text: I thought I knew your Deck, but you keep improving it.

V0509_33_00_01_0.text: This is my strategy for victory!

V0509_33_00_02_0.text: I'm gonna soar through the sky like a bird!

V0509_30_00_02_0.text: Did you really think I'd fall for such an obvious trap?

V0509_34_00_00_0.text: A Duel brings a smile to every child's face.

V0509_34_00_01_0.text:
This is wrong!
Dueling shouldn't be used for war!

V0509_34_00_04_0.text: This... is your most precious card!

V0509_34_00_05_0.text: I wanna Duel as if I'm soaring through the sky!

V0509_34_00_06_0.text:
You didn't Summon a monster... 
I know this strategy.

V0509_34_00_07_0.text: You know how my Lyrilusc Deck works?

V0509_34_00_08_0.text:
I'm brainwashed...?
What are you talking about?

V0509_34_00_09_0.text:
Heh!
I knew you didn't want to lose to me.

V0509_34_00_10_0.text: Instead of chatting, how about making a move?

V0509_34_00_11_0.text: Go ahead and do whatever you like.

V0509_35_00_00_0.text:
I'm Lulu Obsidian.
Let's have fun!

V0509_35_00_01_0.text:
A Duel isn't for war.
It's to make people smile!

V0509_36_00_00_0.text:
We can win this!
Go get 'em!

V0509_36_00_04_0.text: Give it your best shot, Yuto!

V0509_36_00_08_0.text: Don't push yourself too hard, Shay!

V0509_36_00_11_0.text:
I'm sorry...
But I know you'll pull through!

V0509_08_00_00_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Lyrilusc - Bird Call!

V0509_08_00_01_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Lyrilusc - Bird Strike!

V0509_08_00_02_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Spell!
Lyrilusc - Bird Sanctuary!

V0509_08_00_03_0.text: I activate Lyrilusc - Bird Sanctuary's effect!

V0509_08_00_04_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Lyrilusc - Phantom Feathers!

V0509_08_00_05_0.text: I banish Lyrilusc - Phantom Feathers from my Graveyard!

V0509_08_00_06_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, Kahyoreigetsu!

V0509_08_00_07_0.text: Kahyoreigetsu's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0509_08_00_08_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Wing Requital!

V0509_08_00_09_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Swallow's Nest!

V0509_08_00_10_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Summon Storm!

V0509_08_00_11_0.text: I banish Summon Storm from my Graveyard to use its effect!

V0509_08_00_12_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Quill Pen of Gulldos!

V0509_08_00_13_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Jack-In-The-Hand!

V0509_08_00_14_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Where Arf Thou?!

V0509_08_00_15_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, One for One!

V0509_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Icarus Attack!

V0509_08_00_17_0.text: I activate the Trap Card, Spiritual Wind Art - Miyabi!

V0509_09_00_00_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate my Nightingale's effect!

V0509_09_00_01_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Ensemblue Robin's effect!

V0509_09_00_02_0.text: Ensemblue Robin activates when it's sent to the Graveyard!

V0509_09_00_03_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Promenade Thrush's effect!

V0509_09_00_04_0.text: I use my Overlay Units to activate my Thrush's effect!

V0509_09_00_05_0.text: Recital Starling's effect activates when she's Xyz Summoned!

V0509_09_00_06_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Recital Starling's effect!

V0509_09_00_07_0.text: I used an Xyz Lyrilusc to Fusion Summon my Nightingale!

V0509_09_00_09_0.text: Special Summoning Cobalt Sparrow activates her effect!

V0509_09_00_10_0.text: I activate Sapphire Swallow's effect from my hand!

V0509_09_00_11_0.text: Using Sapphire Swallow to Xyz Summon activates her effect!

V0509_09_00_12_0.text: Special Summoning Celestine Wagtail activates her effect!

V0509_09_00_13_0.text: Celestine Wagtail's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0509_09_00_14_0.text: Special Summoning Turquoise Warbler activates her effect!

V0509_09_00_15_0.text: Beryl Canary's effect activates from my hand!

V0509_09_00_16_0.text: Fusion Parasite activates when it's Special Summoned!

V0509_09_00_18_0.text: I Tribute Slower Swallow to activate its effect!

V0509_09_00_19_0.text: I use 2 Overlay Units to play Kikinagashi Fucho's effect!

V0509_09_00_20_0.text: I use 2 Overlay Units to activate Dark Rebellion's effect!

V0509_09_00_21_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Rise Falcon's effect!

V0509_09_00_22_0.text: Raidraptor - Last Strix's effect activates from my hand!

V0509_37_00_00_0.text: My beautiful birds, spread your wings above the battlefield!

V0509_13_00_00_0.text:
From high above!
Rank 1 Lyrilusc - Assembled Nightingale!

V0509_37_00_01_0.text: My beautiful birds, chirp and sing above the battlefield!

V0509_37_00_02_0.text: My beautiful birds, dance above the battlefield!

V0509_37_00_03_0.text: My beautiful birds, harmonize above the battlefield!

V0509_13_00_03_0.text:
Join me!
Rank 1 Lyrilusc - Recital Starling!

V0509_37_00_04_0.text: Look high to the sky as the songbirds sing together as one!

V0509_13_00_11_0.text: I'm going to use Saya's most special card!

V0509_37_00_05_0.text: Cloaked in shadows and relentless in its objective!

V0509_13_00_14_0.text: I can use your help, Yuto!

V0509_13_00_14_1.text:
Rise up!
Rank 4 Dark Rebellion Xyz Dragon!

V0509_37_00_06_0.text:
Soar on wings of courage!
Talons ready for the rebellion!

V0509_13_00_15_1.text: Witness the ascent of Rank 4 Raidraptor - Rise Falcon!

V0509_19_00_01_0.text: Assembled Nightingale attacks for a second time!

V0509_44_00_02_0.text: Only one will rule the Duel...

V0509_44_00_03_0.text: In the ultimate fusion of monsters and mayhem!

V0509_27_00_01_0.text: I can't take more of that...
